{"tid":921654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣播道老牌豪宅 女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-11-29T17:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T00:25:14.000Z","uid":160807,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"698c8026639967ae56cf45658e8117c75df024e3","tid":921654,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181129/large/1543466864_bc70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181129%2Flarge%2F1543466864_bc70.jpg&h=4917c18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龍翔苑有人高處墮下身亡。(張培生攝)<br />\n<br />\n【14:50】女死者姓許55歲，留有遺書；據悉有病患困擾。<br />\n<br />\n九龍塘廣播道龍翔苑，早上11時左右，一名中年女子，由高處墮下倒卧地面。保安員發現後致電報警，由救護員將女事主送廣華醫院，但經搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查，女事主由7樓走廊墮下。<br />\n<br />\n龍翔苑屬於大型屋苑式的低密度豪宅，樓齡近50年，興建之初，是供公務員以優惠價購買，現時可自由出售或租賃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181129/58971683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58971683&d=1LWwu1L6ebsTUj17mC%2FiJP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f8a65062\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58971683&h=68839ba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181129/58971683</a>"},{"pid":"d729eeb566daaddaea9208f6389d875ae3a21492","tid":921654,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:35:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcb9993dfd3bda850391816aff938e81ab96b311","tid":921654,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d729eeb566daaddaea9208f6389d875ae3a21492","tid":921654,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:35:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:49:30.000Z","msg":"7樓走廊"},{"pid":"b2f1b3e5d6a4e648